# Documentation-First Workflow

Before modifying any source file, read its corresponding `docs-src/` documentation first.

## Doc Lookup

| Source path | Documentation path |
|-------------|-------------------|
| `server/src/ws.ts` | `docs-src/server/src/ws.md` |
| `web/src/lib/store.ts` | `docs-src/web/src/lib/store.md` |
| `tests/server/sfu/webrtc-ice.test.ts` | `docs-src/tests/server/sfu/webrtc-ice.md` |

Rule: replace repo root with `docs-src/`, change extension to `.md`. For `*.test.ts`, drop `.test` from the stem.

## After Code Changes

Any behavior change must update the matching `docs-src/` file in the same session.

